---
intent: >
  Refactor aidemd.dev to conform to the coding playbook's on-page SEO depth
  across three pillars — heading structure, accessibility, and metadata —
  closing real drift from the playbook's client/seo.md conventions (semantic
  HTML, ARIA, generateMetadata, JSON-LD, canonical, sitemap). No new features;
  every step enforces a specific playbook rule or a WCAG 2.1 AA requirement
  the Lighthouse ≥95 outcome implicitly demands.
---

